_description: Prayer for Henry VIII, and against Cardinal Wolsey — ten 8-line stanzas in couplets

BLHar2252.First Lines:
God save hyng harry owr nobyll kyngAnd all þat kyn to hym
                    lovyng…
BLHar2252.Last Lines:
…I dar not write vndr my nameffor fere to have to myche
                    blame
